{"tid":2280101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場：《星島》今突公開被釘牌老師教案 疑企圖影響教師上訴結果","createTime":"2020-11-10T08:47:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T11:04:43.000Z","uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c0df9c7eaa0cdec8eae62b2eab3c9f39cabca977","tid":2280101,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T08:47:39.000Z","msg":"九龍塘宣道小學一名教師被指「有計劃地散播港獨」，成為首位被教育局以專業失德為由「釘牌」的教師。《星島日報》今（10 日）獨家公開涉事教案，指內容以錯誤事實引導學生、曲解歷史，又引述不具名小學校長，批評涉事教師鋪排偏頗立場。教協副會長兼教育界立法會議員葉建源對教案外洩感遺憾，強調教師已向當局上訴，「若有人透過洩密企圖影響上訴結果，是不道德做法。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%98%9F%E5%B3%B6-%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E8%A2%AB%E9%87%98%E7%89%8C%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E6%95%99%E6%A1%88-%E8%91%89%E5%BB%BA%E6%BA%90-%E8%8B%A5%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%B4%A9%E5%AF%86%E5%9C%96%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4-%E5%81%9A%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7/?fbclid=IwAR3MGK2iRtw_xXUeFyLFKgDufh9eMRrjFx7tEGbbaW4s8W66ZnGy6LzCpAM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2598%259F%25E5%25B3%25B6-%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%2587%2598%25E7%2589%258C%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E6%25BA%2590-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B4%25A9%25E5%25AF%2586%25E5%259C%2596%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E5%2581%259A%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%2581%2593%25E5%25BE%25B7%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3MGK2iRtw_xXUeFyLFKgDufh9eMRrjFx7tEGbbaW4s8W66ZnGy6LzCpAM&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7ImyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=b280f16a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2598%259F%25E5%25B3%25B6-%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%2587%2598%25E7%2589%258C%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E6%